OL,3,CWoman jailed for life for 'brutal'
OL,4,Cmurder of Caroline Glachan in 1996
OL,6,FThis report contains graphic details
OL,7,Fthat some people may find distressing.
OL,9,FA woman who got away with murder for
OL,10,F27 years has been jailed for killing
OL,11,Fschool girl Caroline Glachan.
OL,13,FDonna Marie Brand, 44, was jailed for
OL,14,Flife and ordered to serve a minimum of
OL,15,F17 years when she appeared at the High
OL,16,FCourt in Glasgow for sentencing on
OL,17,FMonday.
