OL,3,CWoman jailed for life for 'brutal'
OL,4,Cmurder of Caroline Glachan in 1996
OL,6,FShe appeared in court alongside Robert
OL,7,FO'Brien and Andrew Kelly in December,
OL,8,Fof killing O'Brien's 14-year-old
OL,9,Fgirlfriend Caroline in August 1996.
OL,11,FDuring 10 days of evidence, the jury
OL,12,Fheard Caroline was repeatedly punched
OL,13,Fand kicked, and had bricks or similar
OL,14,Fitems thrown at her, causing blunt
OL,15,Fforce trauma to her head and body.
OL,17,FThe trio had arranged to meet Caroline
OL,18,Fat a bridge near the towpath beside
OL,19,Fthe River Leven, between Renton and
OL,20,FBonhill in West Dunbartonshire, on
OL,21,FAugust 25 that year, the trial heard.
