OL,6,FAfter the attack she was pushed or
OL,7,Ffell into undergrowth and her body was
OL,8,Fdiscovered in the river at Place of
OL,9,FBonhill, Renton, later the same day,
OL,10,Fwhich was her mother's 40th birthday.
OL,12,Fat the Glasgow court in January, with
OL,13,FO'Brien ordered to serve a minimum of
OL,14,F22 years behind bars and Kelly handed
OL,15,Fa minimum of 18 years.
OL,17,FBrand could not attend court for
OL,18,Fsentencing in January because she was
OL,19,Fin hospital, and on Monday appeared
OL,20,Ffor sentencing via video link.
