OL,4,Cmurder of Caroline Glachan in 1996
OL,6,FWhen sentencing the two men in
OL,7,FJanuary, judge Lord Braid described
OL,8,Fthe murder as "brutal, depraved and
OL,9,Fabove all wicked".
OL,11,FHe said O'Brien was the main
OL,12,Fperpetrator and used "extreme
OL,13,Fviolence" on Caroline.
OL,15,FThe judge said while Kelly played a
OL,16,Flesser role, he was also involved in
OL,17,Finflicting "murderous violence" on the
OL,18,Fteenager.
