OL,6,FDuring the trial, forensic pathologist
OL,7,FDr Marjorie Turner told the court the
OL,8,F14-year-old was still alive when she
OL,9,Fwent into the water and the ultimate
OL,10,Fcause of death was drowning.
OL,12,FCaroline's mother Margaret McKeich
OL,13,Ftold jurors her daughter was
OL,14,F"infatuated" with O'Brien but she did
OL,15,Fnot approve of the relationship
OL,16,Fbecause he was a few years older.
OL,18,FMrs McKeich said her daughter had
OL,19,Fpreviously disclosed that O'Brien had
OL,20,F"lifted his hands to her".
