OL,6,FSpeaking outside the court, she said
OL,7,Fjustice has been done but she will
OL,8,Falways feel the "void" left by her
OL,9,Fdaughter's death as one of her killers
OL,10,Fwas jailed for at least 17 years.
OL,12,FMs McKeich said: "It was a good
OL,13,Fsentence and it was actually more than
OL,14,FI was expecting, I'm quite pleased,
OL,15,Fnow it's like a weight lifted off my
OL,16,Fshoulders and as I've said before it's
OL,17,Fnot closure, it's justice, we don't
OL,18,Fget closure, it's a void that will not
OL,19,Fever be filled, so you don't get
OL,20,Fclosure.
